								having to involve dev at every little step.
							</p>
							<hr />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-6">
							<h4>Get more ideas to market - faster</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>
									<b>Build, test and update content in minutes</b> - without dev
									support. Iterate faster. Update more often. Respond to market
									changes.
								</li>
