									publishing, using the Ideation Room and in-app collaboration
									and workflows.
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="col-6">
							<h4>Freedom to own the content lifecycle</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>
									<b>Integrate the tools you love</b> - e-Commerce, CRM, SEO,
									personalization, automationâ€¦ anything your business needs.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b>Translate and localize content fast</b> - supporting as many
									versions as you need
								</li>
								<li>
									<b>Deliver content consistently across channels</b> - web, mobile,
									kiosks, apps, and social platforms.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b>View, control, and manage workflows across</b> different users and
									teams for faster collaboration and content approval cycles.
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
